    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) Die lune qui fuit nonus intrantis mensis decembris. <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">Bonorum virorum</rs> presentia quorum
                        nomina inferius scripta invenientur. Domnus <persName
                            key="#Priors #Monasteries" ref="#people/3716">Mathelbertus</persName>, <rs key="#Priors"
                            >prior</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #Houses #Missus"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2075">Sancti Cipriani</orgName>, quod est
                        hedificatum in <geogName key="#Marca/ducatum" ref="#estates/2096"><rs key="#Marca/ducatum"
                                >ducato</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Marca/ducatum #Monasteries" ref="#places/914"
                                >Venetię</placeName></geogName>, sub hobedientie monasterii <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti supra
                            Padum</orgName>, adstante domno <persName key="#Priors #Monasteries"
                            ref="#people/3570">Wili[elm]o</persName>, priore ipsius monasterii
                        Sancti Benedicti, et domno <persName key="#Priors #Monks #Churches" ref="#people/3717"
                            >Adam</persName>, <rs key="#Monks">monacho</rs> ipsius monasterii Sancii
                        Benedieti et prior <rs key="#Churches">ęcclesię</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Priors" ref="#juridical_persons/2416">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName> de <rs key="#Burgi">burgo</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Burgi #Churches" ref="#places/275"
                            >Mantuę</placeName>, investivit <persName
                            key="#Houses #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Wine #childOf #nephew/nieceOf"
                            >Ottobonum</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filium</rs>
                        <persName key="#parentOf">Atonis</persName> de
                            <placeName>Walmate</placeName> eiusque heredes de <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">peciis tribus terre</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Wine">vineis</rs> sive plus sint quę sunt in territorio civitatis
                        Mantuę, et de tribus <rs key="#Houses">casamentis</rs> quę sunt in civitatę
                        predicta, prope <placeName>Turrim Albam</placeName>, quę [pr]ia fuerunt
                            <persName key="#uncle/auntOf #marriage">Oldevrandi</persName>
                        <rs key="#uncle/auntOf">barbani</rs> sui, et ipse Oldevrandus
                            <rs>testamento</rs> reliquid <persName key="#marriage">Utthe</persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxori</rs> sue et ipsa Uttha, pro anima sua et ipsius
                        viri sui, dedit monasterio predicto Sancti Cipriani. Ita quod Ottobonus
                        eiusque heredes habere et tenere debent, et omni anno in festivitate sancti
                        Martini vel octavo die antea aut postea tribuere debent <rs>denarios duos
                            Veronensis monete</rs> pro ficto predicto priore [Sancti C]ipriani et
                        eius successoribus vel eorum <rs key="#Missus">misso</rs> in ha[c] civitatec
                        Mantua, tali modo quod liceat eidem [Ott]obono eiusque heredibus, secundum
                        usum Mantuę, vendere ad predictum fictum reddendum monasterio ut superius
                        legitur. Et si vendere voluerint domino petere debent terre vendere ad
                        duodecim denarios minus quam alii, et si autem noluerint, tunc licitum esse
                        debet Ottobono et eius heredibus vendendi eas si voluerint ad predictum
                        fictum reddendum, ut supra legitur, excepto aecclesię et servo. Actum est
                        hoc in refectorio Sancti Martini, burgi Mantuę. Anno dominice incarnationis
                        Millesimo Centesimo quadragesimo, predicto die, inditione tercia.
                        [Inte]rfuerunt ibi <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"
                            >Otto</persName> de Gurgolato, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Sigefredus</persName> de Sancta
                        Agatha, <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Raginerius
                            Buca</persName> de Surico, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Furnus</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Lanfrancus</persName> de Brisia,
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Albertus</persName> de
                        Rivarioli, <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Albertus
                            Miccus</persName>, et rogati sunt <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (SN)
                        Ego <persName key="#Notary #Writer">Bonus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> his interfui, rogatus <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scripsi</rs>. </ab>
